::Aerotaur::
       "Hmm...?"  He thinks for a moment.  "Yes, I suppose there was that one 
that Flicker killed during his escape.  Which I might add," he turns back to 
Flicker, "was poorly planned.  You probably could have walked out without 
anyone noticing.  I doubt anyone has noticed my absence yet."
